<br />

<br />
We had a couple of those guys in guild until recently that did nothing but number crunch the game into obscene proportions.  They maintained SCM3 was 30 pct and few believed them, so take the following bit at face value:
<br />

<br />
According to the 'description' of SCM, it was a random pct save each cast, with the max pct being raised for higher levels.  They quoted research done on other boards (I'm thinking eqcleric, but could be wrong) that proved it was a fixed amount each cast.
<br />

<br />
Just didn't hear anyone mention it, so thought I'd throw that out.
<br />

<br />
LONG LIVE AMBIGUOUS DATA!
<br />

<br />
