				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My tests showed no randomness to the savings, within a 0.5 percent margin of error.  When you do your tests make sure you have lich and other mana regen off.  Also, take off all your armor to make the percentages more easily visible, and use a spell that takes a large amount of mana.
<br />

<br />
I'm rather annoyed that my old post on this stuff was deleted.   I'm hoping I kept it around somewhere and will resubmit it.
